+    /**
+     * Returns the Base64URL encoding of the specified elliptic curve 'x',
+     * 'y' or 'd' coordinate, with leading zero padding up to the specified
+     * field size in bits.
+     * Copied and adapted from nimbus-jose-jwt (ECKey#encodeCoordinate)
